name: 25 Botanics
description: Through the study of nature, “The Inner Earth” has a comprehensive knowledge of beneficial herbs, though a notable number of advanced countries have started relying more on technology than traditional methods. This has left a divide in the Botanics field, with some practitioners eager to prove their superiority over technology, and others just happy to help when needed. Rumor has it that some practitioners have even been looking to ancient and lost techniques.
